snippet.title: G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX x Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Check out multiplayer action in this latest trailer for G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra, an upcoming retro side-scrolling beat 'em up game. Cobra returns once again with its most fiendish plot yet and it's up to G.I. JOE to defeat them once more! Pick one of the real American heroes, gear up, and get straight into the fight. G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra is coming to PC.
